Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.00,0:00:02.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Yayu hurriedly entered the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.82,0:00:05.30,Default,,0,0,0,,He took out photos from high school and checked them one by one.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.58,0:00:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,He realized that one of them was his old classmate Siwoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.38,0:00:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Feeling delighted, he tried to suggest that Siwoo stop by for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:12.88,Default,,0,0,0,,But Siwoo said.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.02,0:00:15.40,Default,,0,0,0,,He said he had to deliver another order.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:19.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Not wanting to waste time, the two just exchanged light greetings.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.86,0:00:22.14,Default,,0,0,0,,And then Siwoo quickly left.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.38,0:00:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Returning to the room, Yayu felt more and more regret as he thought about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.32,0:00:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Now approaching thirty, his appearance had not changed much since his school days.
